Postgres superuser default name: postgres

Starting/stopping server
	Single user mode:
	/etc/init.d/postgres start/stop

	Multiuser mode (pq superuser must execute)
	postmaster -D datadir (e.g. '/var/lib/pgsql')

PQ commands

createuser username
createdb dbname
dropdb	dbname
psql	dbname


psql

\h				help
\g or ;			end input
drop database dbname

comments
	--			single line
	/* ... */	multi line


